          </subparagraph>
          <subparagraph id="HA66A8A106E5E413CB4B519D15CDDDB9B">
            <enum>(M)</enum>
            <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The table of sections for <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/ch:1/sch:A/pt:IV/spt:C">subpart C of part IV of subchapter A of chapter 1 of such Code</cato:entity-ref> is amended by inserting after the item relating to <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:36B">section 36B</cato:entity-ref> the following new item:</text>
